-value=\"0\" data-delimiter=\" \">0<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-counter-number-suffix\"><\/span>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-adfbfba elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"adfbfba\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Parmi les associations accompagn\u00e9es : R\u00e8gles \u00c9l\u00e9mentaires, Clasches, CFCV, OVSESE.\u200b<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fb7a8f6 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"fb7a8f6\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3735d6e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3735d6e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Les associations ayant besoin d&rsquo;un soutien juridique dans le cadre de la d\u00e9fense des droits des femmes peuvent solliciter la Force Juridique.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bfbc76f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"bfbc76f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f872942 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f872942\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Contacts<\/h4>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-432b100 lien-hypertexte elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"432b100\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><a href=\"mailto:forcejuridique@fondationdesfemmes.org\">forcejuridique@fondationdesfemmes.org<\/a><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d3064ba e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"d3064ba\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8cbcd7d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"8cbcd7d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-16a08cc e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"16a08cc\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b4e3274 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b4e3274\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Think Tank : \n<br>produire une doctrine du<span class=\"highlight-jaune\">droit<\/span> f\u00e9ministe<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7c7d8d2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7c7d8d2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Au-del\u00e0 de son r\u00f4le de soutien juridique, la Force Juridique fonctionne comme un think tank f\u00e9ministe : un lieu de r\u00e9flexion, de production intellectuelle et d&rsquo;\u00e9laboration de doctrine du droit f\u00e9ministe.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8a10f28 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"8a10f28\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-129ab2b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"129ab2b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Dans ce cadre, elle coordonne des articles, notes de position, guides pratiques, conf\u00e9rences et d\u00e9bats, qui visent \u00e0 rendre le droit plus accessible, compr\u00e9hensible et efficace pour les femmes, les associations et les d\u00e9cideur\u00b7ses publics.<br \/><br \/>Les travaux du think tank portent notamment sur des th\u00e9matiques cl\u00e9s comme la sant\u00e9 des femmes, l&rsquo;\u00e9galit\u00e9 professionnelle, la lutte contre les violences sexistes et sexuelles, le droit de la famille et les enjeux juridiques contemporains li\u00e9s \u00e0 l&rsquo;\u00e9galit\u00e9 femmes-hommes.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0878f75 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"0878f75\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c1d6f95 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"c1d6f95\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-af29a70 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"af29a70\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-70a61ef e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"70a61ef\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d701bc4 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d701bc4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Comment b\u00e9n\u00e9ficier du <span class=\"highlight-vert\">soutien<\/span> de la fondation des femmes<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-de2e49a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"de2e49a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-742e661 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"742e661\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>La Fondation des Femmes est la structure de r\u00e9f\u00e9rence en France pour la libert\u00e9 et les droits des femmes et pour la lutte contre les violences dont elles sont victimes.<br \/>Gr\u00e2ce aux dons qu&rsquo;elle re\u00e7oit, la Fondation des Femmes apporte son soutien aux initiatives associatives \u00e0 fort impact, remplissant les crit\u00e8res suivants :<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e442771 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e442771\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7762ade text-pretty elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7762ade\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Crit\u00e8res g\u00e9n\u00e9raux d\u2019\u00e9ligibilit\u00e9 :<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1b5256d e-con-full e-grid elementor-hidden-tablet elementor-hidden-mobile e-con e-child\" data-id=\"1b5256d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element element